# Inbox

Dump anything here — reminders, notes for meetings, ideas, personal tasks. {{INSTANCE_NAME}} processes this file every run and routes entries to the right place.

**Routing hints** (optional — {{INSTANCE_NAME}} will figure it out, but these help):
- Mention a meeting name → goes to that meeting's "Next Session Notes"
- `personal:` prefix → creates a personal task entity
- `idea:` / `research:` prefix → goes to research queue
- Everything else → action item

